{
  "name": "easy-prompt-ai",
  "displayName": "Easy Prompt — AI 智能 Prompt 增强器",
  "description": "两步 AI 意图识别 + 97 个专业场景 + 10 大用户画像，将简单描述扩写为专业 Prompt。配套 PromptHub 精选库（zhiz.chat）。Two-step AI intent routing with 97 scenes & 10 personas for professional prompt generation. Includes PromptHub curated library (zhiz.chat). (VSCode / IntelliJ / Browser / Web).",
  "version": "5.3.8",
  "publisher": "FlippySun",
  "license": "MIT",
  "engines": {
    "vscode": "^1.85.0"
  },
  "categories": [
    "Other",
    "Machine Learning"
  ],
  "keywords": [
    "prompt",
    "ai",
    "copilot",
    "gpt",
    "gemini",
    "prompt engineering"
  ],
  "repository": {
    "type": "git",
    "url": "https://github.com/FlippySun/Easy-Prompt"
  },
  "icon": "assets/images/logo-vscode@128x128.png",
  "activationEvents": [
    "onStartupFinished",
    "onUri"
  ],
  "main": "./extension.js",
  "contributes": {
    "commands": [
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.enhanceSelected",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 增强选中文本",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.smartEnhance",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 智能增强",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.enhanceInput",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 快速输入增强",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.showScenes",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 浏览场景列表",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.enhanceWithScene",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 指定场景增强",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.showWelcome",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 查看使用教程",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.configureApi",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 配置自定义 API",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.statusBarMenu",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 打开快捷菜单",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.showHistory",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 查看增强历史",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.ssoLogin",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 登录 zhiz.chat",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.ssoLogout",
        "title": "Easy Prompt: 退出登录",
        "category": "Easy Prompt"
      }
    ],
    "keybindings": [
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.enhanceSelected",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+p",
        "mac": "ctrl+alt+p"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.smartEnhance",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+i",
        "mac": "ctrl+alt+i"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.enhanceInput",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+o",
        "mac": "ctrl+alt+o"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.showScenes",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+l",
        "mac": "ctrl+alt+l"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.enhanceWithScene",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+m",
        "mac": "ctrl+alt+m"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.showWelcome",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+h",
        "mac": "ctrl+alt+h"
      },
      {
        "command": "easy-prompt.showHistory",
        "key": "ctrl+alt+y",
        "mac": "ctrl+alt+y"
      }
    ],
    "configuration": {
      "title": "Easy Prompt",
      "properties": {
        "easyPrompt.apiMode": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "enum": [
            "",
            "openai",
            "openai-responses",
            "claude",
            "gemini"
          ],
          "enumDescriptions": [
            "自动检测（根据 API 路径推断）",
            "OpenAI Chat Completions API 兼容",
            "OpenAI Responses API 兼容",
            "Claude API 兼容",
            "Google Gemini API 兼容"
          ],
          "markdownDescription": "API 协议模式。\n\n**留空 = 自动检测**。不同的 AI 服务商使用不同的 API 协议，选择对应模式以确保正确通信。建议通过命令面板 `Easy Prompt: 配置自定义 API` 来配置。",
          "order": 1
        },
        "easyPrompt.apiBaseUrl": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "markdownDescription": "自定义 API Base URL（完整地址，包含协议和路径）。\n\n**留空 = 使用内置免费服务**。建议通过命令面板 `Easy Prompt: 配置自定义 API` 来配置，支持一键测试。\n\n> ⚠️ 此项为兼容旧版保留，新版建议分别配置 API Host 和 API Path。",
          "order": 2
        },
        "easyPrompt.apiHost": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "markdownDescription": "API 服务器地址（仅协议+域名+端口，如 `https://api.openai.com`）。\n\n**留空 = 使用内置免费服务**。建议通过命令面板 `Easy Prompt: 配置自定义 API` 来配置。",
          "order": 3
        },
        "easyPrompt.apiPath": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "markdownDescription": "API 路径（如 `/v1/chat/completions`）。\n\n**留空 = 使用所选模式的默认路径**。切换 API 模式时会自动填充默认路径。",
          "order": 4
        },
        "easyPrompt.apiKey": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "markdownDescription": "自定义 API Key。\n\n**留空 = 使用内置免费服务**，无需任何配置。如需自定义，建议通过命令面板 `Easy Prompt: 配置自定义 API` 来配置，支持测试验证后再保存。",
          "order": 5
        },
        "easyPrompt.model": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "enum": [
            "",
            "claude-opus-4-6",
            "claude-sonnet-4-5",
            "claude-haiku-4-5",
            "claude-opus-4-1",
            "claude-sonnet-4",
            "gpt-5.4",
            "gpt-5.3-codex",
            "gpt-5.2",
            "gpt-5.2-pro",
            "gpt-5-mini",
            "gpt-5-nano",
            "gpt-5",
            "gpt-4.1",
            "gpt-4.1-mini",
            "gpt-4o",
            "gpt-4o-mini",
            "o3",
            "o4-mini",
            "gemini-3-pro-preview",
            "gemini-3-flash-preview",
            "gemini-3.0-pro",
            "gemini-2.5-pro",
            "gemini-2.5-flash",
            "deepseek-v3.2-chat",
            "deepseek-v3.2-reasoner",
            "deepseek-r1",
            "grok-4",
            "grok-3",
            "glm-5",
            "glm-4.7",
            "kimi-k2.5",
            "kimi-k2",
            "qwen3-max",
            "qwen3-235b",
            "minimax-m2.5"
          ],
          "enumDescriptions": [
            "🎯 使用内置默认模型（gpt-5.4）",
            "Anthropic Claude Opus 4.6 — 最智能（需自定义 API）",
            "Anthropic Claude Sonnet 4.5 — 速度与智能平衡（需自定义 API）",
            "Anthropic Claude Haiku 4.5 — 最快速（需自定义 API）",
            "Anthropic Claude Opus 4.1 — 上一代旗舰（需自定义 API）",
            "Anthropic Claude Sonnet 4 — 上一代均衡（需自定义 API）",
            "OpenAI GPT-5.2 — 最新旗舰（需自定义 API）",
            "OpenAI GPT-5.2 Pro — 更智能更精准（需自定义 API）",
            "OpenAI GPT-5 mini — 快速高效",
            "OpenAI GPT-5 nano — 极致性价比",
            "OpenAI GPT-5",
            "OpenAI GPT-4.1 — 最智能非推理模型",
            "OpenAI GPT-4.1 mini — 轻量快速版（需自定义 API）",
            "OpenAI GPT-4o — 灵活智能",
            "OpenAI GPT-4o mini — 经济实惠（需自定义 API）",
            "OpenAI o3 — 复杂推理",
            "OpenAI o4-mini — 快速推理",
            "Google Gemini 3 Pro Preview — 最强多模态",
            "Google Gemini 3 Flash Preview — 速度与智能",
            "Google Gemini 3.0 Pro",
            "Google Gemini 2.5 Pro — 高级思维",
            "Google Gemini 2.5 Flash — 高性价比（需自定义 API）",
            "DeepSeek V3.2 Chat — 通用对话",
            "DeepSeek V3.2 Reasoner — 深度推理",
            "DeepSeek R1 — 推理模型",
            "xAI Grok 4",
            "xAI Grok 3",
            "智谱 GLM-5",
            "智谱 GLM-4.7",
            "Kimi K2.5",
            "Kimi K2",
            "通义千问 Qwen3 Max",
            "通义千问 Qwen3 235B",
            "MiniMax M2.5"
          ],
          "markdownDescription": "自定义模型名称。\n\n**留空 = 使用内置默认模型**。从下拉列表选择常用模型，或在 `settings.json` 中手动填写其他模型名。\n\n> 💡 在 API 配置面板中可使用「获取模型」按钮自动获取可用模型列表。",
          "order": 6
        },
        "easyPrompt.enhanceMode": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "fast",
          "enum": [
            "fast",
            "deep"
          ],
          "enumDescriptions": [
            "Fast（默认）— 保持当前模型与接口不变，第二步输出更精炼",
            "Deep — 保持当前模型与接口不变，第二步输出更完整"
          ],
          "markdownDescription": "Prompt 增强模式。\n\n**Fast（默认）**：保持当前模型与 API 接口不变，只让第二步生成更精炼、更短。\n\n**Deep**：保持当前模型与 API 接口不变，只让第二步生成更完整、更充分。\n\n> 该设置不会自动切换模型，也不会修改请求路径；尤其在 Browser 端会尽量保持请求形状稳定。",
          "order": 7
        },
        "easyPrompt.language": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": [
            "zh-CN",
            "en"
          ],
          "default": "zh-CN",
          "description": "界面语言",
          "order": 8
        },
        "easyPrompt.backendMode": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": [
            "auto",
            "backend-only",
            "local-only"
          ],
          "default": "auto",
          "markdownDescription": "后端 AI 服务模式。\n\n**auto（默认）**：优先后端 API，失败自动回退本地直连。\n\n**backend-only**：仅使用后端 API，不回退（后端不可用时报错）。\n\n**local-only**：仅使用本地直连 AI API（完全不连后端）。",
          "order": 9
        },
        "easyPrompt.backendUrl": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "https://api.zhiz.chat",
          "markdownDescription": "后端 API 服务地址。\n\n**默认**：`https://api.zhiz.chat`。仅在自建后端时需要修改。",
          "order": 10
        },
        "easyPrompt.backendToken": {
          "type": "string",
          "default": "",
          "markdownDescription": "后端 Access Token（手动输入）。\n\n登录 `zhiz.chat` 后在个人设置中获取。留空则以匿名身份使用（受更严格限流）。",
          "order": 11
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "scripts": {
    "package": "npx @vscode/vsce package",
    "install-ext": "code --install-extension easy-prompt-*.vsix",
    "browser:dev": "npm --prefix browser run dev",
    "browser:dev:firefox": "npm --prefix browser run dev:firefox",
    "browser:dev:safari": "npm --prefix browser run dev:safari",
    "browser:build": "npm --prefix browser run build",
    "browser:build:firefox": "npm --prefix browser run build:firefox",
    "browser:build:safari": "npm --prefix browser run build:safari",
    "browser:zip": "npm --prefix browser run zip",
    "browser:zip:firefox": "npm --prefix browser run zip:firefox",
    "browser:zip:safari": "npm --prefix browser run zip:safari",
    "browser:install": "npm --prefix browser install",
    "browser:typecheck": "npm --prefix browser run typecheck",
    "browser:safari:convert": "npm --prefix browser run safari:convert",
    "browser:safari:convert:dry-run": "npm --prefix browser run safari:convert:dry-run",
    "browser:build:all": "npm --prefix browser run build:all",
    "browser:zip:all": "npm --prefix browser run zip:all",
    "browser:test:unit": "npm --prefix browser run test:unit",
    "test:parity": "node tests/test-parity.js",
    "test:integration": "node tests/test-backend-integration.js"
  }
}
